high_descs: Turn right, when you reach the wall, turn left. When leaving the room, turn right. Passing the sofa, turn right. Turn right between the sofa and the coffee table.  Turn left, approach the coffee table, turn left.

Turn left, turn right, turn left. After passing the sofa, turn left, after passing the table where the microwave is, turn right. After passing the table, turn right. Go to the wall, turn left. Approach the sink.
Place the ladle over the sink. Open the faucet for 4 seconds, close the faucet. Take the ladle.
Place the ladle to the left on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Find a ladle, wet it and place it on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffee table.
Take the serving spoon from the coffee table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the serving spoon into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the counter top.
Put the serving spoon on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Placed the serving spoon on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn right go straight to the coffee table
Pick the spoon from the coffee table
Turn left go straight walk to the sink
Put the spoon into the sink rinse it off and take it back
Turn around to the counter top
Place the spoon on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Pick the spoon from the coffee table, clean it and place it on the counter top
